  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/d160cfe79552f1b8f1aa71b25fd56013.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/c8bc474b0b0d897f174b964f8b1ca0b6.poster.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/c8bc474b0b0d897f174b964f8b1ca0b6.webm?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/c8bc474b0b0d897f174b964f8b1ca0b6.mp4?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Treze Trilhas is home to the St. Dinfna Hotel, a decadent site that is the subject of numerous rumors including mysterious disappearances and paranormal activity. Hoping to break the story, amateur journalist Roberto Leite Lopes travels to Santa Catarina following a tip from his friend Stephanie.<br><br>His investigative skills will be needed not only to uncover the truth but to survive when reality is turned upside down with his discovery of a camera that reveals different timelines, a fanatical cult, human experiments, and apparitions roaming the halls. Solve puzzles and scavenge for anything to stop their hunt as the past, present and future collide.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/b51e86bd7580d74a4e571805bd2125b4.poster.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/b51e86bd7580d74a4e571805bd2125b4.webm?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/b51e86bd7580d74a4e571805bd2125b4.mp4?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/413c5fbfb64051e57084e7403af8fa05.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>•\tExplore a Grand Hotel – The Unreal Engine brings terrifyingly realistic visuals to this first-person horror experience.<br>•\tSurvive the Horrors – Scavenge for supplies while you run, hide, or fight the monsters that stalk the corridors.<br>•\tUnravel the Mystery – Worlds collide in a twisting narrative full of puzzles and conspiracies.<br>•\tLook to the past and the future – Interact with different timelines using an enigmatic camera that connects parallel realities to uncover the many secrets hidden in the walls of the hotel.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/33ca8507a0287e5d09c1ec63cce60c07.poster.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/33ca8507a0287e5d09c1ec63cce60c07.webm?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/33ca8507a0287e5d09c1ec63cce60c07.mp4?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join the Discord</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/d160cfe79552f1b8f1aa71b25fd56013.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/c8bc474b0b0d897f174b964f8b1ca0b6.poster.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/c8bc474b0b0d897f174b964f8b1ca0b6.webm?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/c8bc474b0b0d897f174b964f8b1ca0b6.mp4?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Treze Trilhas is home to the St. Dinfna Hotel, a decadent site that is the subject of numerous rumors including mysterious disappearances and paranormal activity. Hoping to break the story, amateur journalist Roberto Leite Lopes travels to Santa Catarina following a tip from his friend Stephanie.<br><br>His investigative skills will be needed not only to uncover the truth but to survive when reality is turned upside down with his discovery of a camera that reveals different timelines, a fanatical cult, human experiments, and apparitions roaming the halls. Solve puzzles and scavenge for anything to stop their hunt as the past, present and future collide.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/b51e86bd7580d74a4e571805bd2125b4.poster.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/b51e86bd7580d74a4e571805bd2125b4.webm?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https